  <compounddef id="group__pinctrl__sf32lb52x" kind="group">
    <compoundname>pinctrl_sf32lb52x</compoundname>
    <title>SiFli SF32LB52x pin control helpers</title>
    <innerfile refid="sf32lb52x-pinctrl_8h">sf32lb52x-pinctrl.h</innerfile>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Macros for pin control configuration of SiFli SF32LB52x. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The macros follow the following naming convention: <computeroutput>&lt;PAD&gt;_&lt;SIGNAL&gt;</computeroutput>.</para>
<para>For example, <computeroutput>PA19_USART1_TXD</computeroutput> corresponds to the <computeroutput>USART1_TXD</computeroutput> signal routed to pad <computeroutput>PA19</computeroutput>.</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#include<sp/>&lt;zephyr/dt-bindings/pinctrl/sifli/sf32lb52x-pinctrl.h&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">&amp;pinctrl<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>usart1_default:<sp/>usart1_default<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>group1<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>pinmux<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;PA19_USART1_TXD&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>group2<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>pinmux<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;PA18_USART1_RXD&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>input-enable;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>bias-pull-up;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
  </compounddef>
